---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Privacy Policy"
  description="Privacy Policy for Idearigs — how we collect, use, and protect your personal data in compliance with the UK GDPR."
>
  <section class="pt-36 pb-20 bg-white">
    <div class="container-custom">
      <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto">

        <!-- Header -->
        <div class="mb-12">
          <span class="inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 bg-accent/10 text-accent text-xs font-bold px-3 py-1 rounded-full uppercase tracking-wide mb-5">Legal</span>
          <h1 class="text-4xl font-black text-gray-900 mb-3">Privacy Policy</h1>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-400">Last Updated: April 6, 2026</p>
        </div>

        <!-- Intro -->
        <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed mb-10">
          At Idearigs, we respect your privacy. This policy explains how we handle your information in compliance with the UK General Data Protection Regulation (UK GDPR) and the Data Protection Act 2018.
        </p>

        <!-- Sections -->
        <div class="space-y-10">

          <div>
            <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3">1. Data We Collect</h2>
            <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed mb-4">We collect minimal personal data to provide our services:</p>
            <ul class="space-y-2 pl-5 list-disc text-gray-600">
              <li><strong class="text-gray-800">Contact Info:</strong> Name and email address.</li>
              <li><strong class="text-gray-800">Technical Info:</strong> Server IP addresses and access credentials (stored encrypted).</li>
              <li><strong class="text-gray-800">Billing Info:</strong> Handled securely by <strong class="text-gray-800">Lemon Squeezy</strong>. We do not store your credit card details.</li>
              <li><strong class="text-gray-800">Usage Data:</strong> Basic analytics (page visits, session duration) collected anonymously to improve our website.</li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <div>
            <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3">2. How We Use Your Data</h2>
            <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed mb-4">Your data is used strictly for:</p>
            <ul class="space-y-2 pl-5 list-disc text-gray-600">
              <li>Monitoring your server health and delivering managed services.</li>
              <li>Contacting you regarding maintenance windows, security alerts, or service updates.</li>
              <li>Processing your monthly subscription and issuing invoices.</li>
              <li>Responding to enquiries submitted through our contact form.</li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <div>
            <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3">3. Legal Basis for Processing</h2>
            <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed mb-4">We process your personal data under the following lawful bases:</p>
            <ul class="space-y-2 pl-5 list-disc text-gray-600">
              <li><strong class="text-gray-800">Contract:</strong> Processing is necessary to deliver the services you have subscribed to.</li>
              <li><strong class="text-gray-800">Legitimate Interests:</strong> To maintain service security, prevent fraud, and improve our platform.</li>
              <li><strong class="text-gray-800">Consent:</strong> For any marketing communications (you may withdraw consent at any time).</li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <div>
            <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3">4. Data Storage and Security</h2>
            <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
              Server credentials are stored using industry-standard AES-256 encryption. Access is restricted to authorised Idearigs personnel only. We do not sell or share your data with third parties, except for the tools necessary to provide the service (e.g., Better Stack for monitoring, Lemon Squeezy for billing). All third-party processors are bound by data processing agreements.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div>
            <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3">5. Data Retention</h2>
            <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
              We retain your personal data for as long as your subscription is active and for up to 6 years thereafter, as required for accounting and legal compliance purposes. Credentials are deleted within 30 days of service termination upon request.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div>
            <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3">6. Your Rights</h2>
            <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed mb-4">
              Under the UK GDPR, you have the right to:
            </p>
            <ul class="space-y-2 pl-5 list-disc text-gray-600">
              <li><strong class="text-gray-800">Access</strong> the personal data we hold about you.</li>
              <li><strong class="text-gray-800">Rectify</strong> any inaccurate or incomplete data.</li>
              <li><strong class="text-gray-800">Erase</strong> your data ("right to be forgotten") where it is no longer necessary.</li>
              <li><strong class="text-gray-800">Restrict</strong> processing in certain circumstances.</li>
              <li><strong class="text-gray-800">Data portability</strong> — receive your data in a structured, machine-readable format.</li>
              <li><strong class="text-gray-800">Object</strong> to processing based on legitimate interests.</li>
            </ul>
            <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed mt-4">
              To exercise any of these rights, please contact us at{' '}
              <a href="mailto:hello@idearigs.com" class="text-accent font-semibold hover:underline">hello@idearigs.com</a>.
              We will respond within 30 days.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div>
            <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3">7. Third-Party Services</h2>
            <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
              We use <strong class="text-gray-800">Lemon Squeezy</strong> as our payment processor and Merchant of Record. Please refer to{' '}
              <a href="https://www.lemonsqueezy.com/privacy" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-accent font-semibold hover:underline">Lemon Squeezy's Privacy Policy</a>{' '}
              for details on how they handle your payment data. We use{' '}
              <strong class="text-gray-800">Better Stack</strong> for server uptime monitoring; data shared with them is limited to server IP addresses and response codes.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div>
            <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3">8. Cookies</h2>
            <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
              Our website uses only essential cookies required for the site to function (e.g., session state). We do not use advertising or tracking cookies. You can control cookie settings through your browser at any time.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div>
            <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3">9. Changes to This Policy</h2>
            <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
              We may update this Privacy Policy periodically. We will notify active subscribers of material changes by email. The "Last Updated" date at the top of this page will always reflect the most recent revision.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div>
            <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3">10. Complaints</h2>
            <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
              If you are unhappy with how we handle your data, you have the right to lodge a complaint with the{' '}
              <strong class="text-gray-800">Information Commissioner's Office (ICO)</strong> at{' '}
              <a href="https://ico.org.uk" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-accent font-semibold hover:underline">ico.org.uk</a>.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div>
            <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3">11. Contact</h2>
            <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
              For any privacy-related questions or requests, please contact our data controller at{' '}
              <a href="mailto:hello@idearigs.com" class="text-accent font-semibold hover:underline">hello@idearigs.com</a>.
            </p>
          </div>

        </div>

        <!-- Divider -->
        <div class="mt-14 pt-8 border-t border-gray-100 flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-start sm:items-center justify-between gap-4">
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-400">© {new Date().getFullYear()} Idearigs. All rights reserved.</p>
          <a href="/terms" class="text-sm text-accent font-semibold hover:underline">Terms and Conditions →</a>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
